Malice scoffed and dropped from the air to land.  His weapons were not rated to take on such heavily armored foes.  Perhaps he should have taken the job in Atlantis.  

&quot;Hmpt.  If megatron were here he&#39;d have blown the place up already.  But he&#39;s playing diplomat,&quot; Malice said as he transformed and hovered in place.

&quot;I only bow to Megatron, true leader of the Decepticons, and this fool Hydras, comes up very short.  If you were smart, you would return to him.&quot;



